OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nearly 1.5 million customers have been 
OL,6, hit in just two weeks by energy firms  
OL,7, collapsing under soaring gas prices.   
OL,9,FAvro Energy and Green ceased trading on
OL,10,FWednesday and their 830,000 combined   
OL,11,Fcustomers face being switched to a new,
OL,12,Fpotentially more expensive, provider.  
OL,14,FGreen's boss, Peter McGirr, told the   
OL,15,FBBC he had done nothing wrong and said 
OL,16,Fbigger firms would soon face problems. 
OL,18,FHowever, the government has cooled on  
OL,19,Fthe idea of loans to the industry, says
OL,20,FBBC business editor Simon Jack.        
